@Private public class MasterRpcServicesVersionWrapper extends Object implements org.apache.hadoop.hbase.shaded.protobuf.generated.RegionServerStatusProtos.RegionServerStatusService.BlockingInterface
A wrapper class for MasterRpcServices shortcut that ensures a client version is available to the callee without a current RPC call.
